By":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T23:58:33.000Z","msg":"講時事政治，無論你點睇，都實有真假膠係又反，唔係又反。<br />\n入黎想輕鬆應該多過想挑機掛<br />\n就算其他forum 都係咁咖啦<br />\n如果要對時事政治都好鐘意討論你應該上左年紀/無乜節目的中老年"},{"pid":"e432d77072f749f148c95644c468f6468778150a","tid":360123,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:08:53.000Z","msg":"黃人優越主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n種族歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廣東話沙文主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大華夏膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adabe6a2f0bac8e9d0c20690527d2f10fa2cb767","tid":360123,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連登仔真係中二病到爆炸<br />\n呢個世界邊度唔係娛樂係多D人留意<br />\n自己<span style=\"color: red;\">政治上腦</span>就要全世界跟你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知邊度睇埋D ON9野以為鍾意政治就係好<br />\n咁不如就鏟晒其他台得番時事台咪得囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明身邊發生啲嘢係關你事<br />\n大家都可以完全唔在乎<br />\n明明對你地有極大影響<br />\n反而只會關心一啲對你哋極少影響又或者根本唔關你事嘅芝麻綠豆嘅花生小事<br />\n人哋只不過係叫你關心下一下依家社會發生嘅事<br />\n就話人哋政治上腦<br />\n垃圾<br />\n講完</blockquote><br />\n你睇睇呢到就知香港人性格<br />\n義佢無意義既事無做囉</blockquote><br />\n最重要嘅係明明身邊發生嘅事係好大件事影響好大<br />\n但係依然仲係一無所知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地唔係唔知<br />\n係睇透, 覺得呢d野由回歸都睇穿<br />\n已經唔想理</blockquote><br />\n唔係睇透 係根本就唔想理/唔知咩事<br />\n呢度個年齡層都係15-25歲嘅人較多<br />\n回歸果陣佢哋都係啱啱出世/未出世<br />\n依家個教育方法同以前有唔少分別<br />\n仲有唔少個心態都係人云亦云<br />\n比傳媒帶住走 個風氣變咗由傳媒主宰<br />\n加上個個都只係活係自己個水晶球入面<br />\n唔會去理水晶球以外發生嘅事<br />\n所以佢哋寧願去關心吓啲小事好過"},{"pid":"d43c2d595851658ed9e1652cf645a043977521cc","tid":360123,"uid":37064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:12:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0627ec20dd91062a4569287771f6e62c4786739f","tid":360123,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>批評好易容<br />\n<br />\n做實事先係最難<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開post然後一直鳩講有咩用 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我喜歡香港呢個地方，實事我亦會做<br />\n<br />\n在網絡世界見到不良風氣自然要出<span style=\"color: red;\">声</span>，如果見到不義不發聲如同行惡，你覺得咁係鳩講係你ge事<br />\n但如果鳩講你都唔願意做，香港會變得更好咩?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那狗現形"},{"pid":"b1becac29ba4254833cd1b8ceaaee8391487119f","tid":360123,"uid":114094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇住啲人係政治Post 細路仔嗌交有時真是忍不住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己咁戇鳩要其共人戇鳩埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n岩聽=同路人<br />\n唔岩聽=五毛<br />\n<br />\n有時d post 十九幾頁都係互屌五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲話自己追求民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 持不同意見就屌人五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾你地鍵到國咪又係獨裁者<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你堆毒撚咁廢實鍵唔到國</s