":7192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:31:18.000Z","msg":"而家連登開正經post唔會有人理"},{"pid":"773a6bbe3ba2122547cc860b5a97c7bb34228b58","tid":360123,"uid":26322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得如果要改善連登第一步就刪咗感情台同埋成人台，肅清班垃圾<br />\n<br />\n連燈之所以無人敢打錯字，都係大家屌得多姐，希望各位巴絲大大力屌柒啲垃圾post</blockquote><br />\n支持肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13aa9736e1bf7183e54229273976e61e418b810f","tid":360123,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"你有好野有討論價值咪入黎囉，你老尾要人玻璃心變大陸狗咩"},{"pid":"dedba94c513b29747dd36bb03e36a9225e8e2306","tid":360123,"uid":26322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家連登開正經post唔會有人理</blockquote><br />\n咩而家，不嬲都無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1747c64dd0ff65a33ba3a8dedac9273ba37b02a7","tid":360123,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"已經証實左樓主係支那狗來<br />\n大家可以走<br />\n由此可知支那會不斷搵五毛踩港<br />\n仲要扮晒恨鐵不成鋼"},{"pid":"7e62834474f0e0d3a9c55e4611d2e0460327773b","tid":360123,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:45:31.000Z","msg":"個論壇背後有堆人係到維穩"},{"pid":"7b30bbf013243502cf181602becb35ec3178a764","tid":360123,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:48:00.000Z","msg":"唔係垃圾，係臘鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a552c9116daa4b2c999825275cb6d3119494a4c","tid":360123,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:50:25.000Z","msg":"根本同呢班人講黎都哂氣"},{"pid":"56e273334d28804d99d239658401648093335024","tid":360123,"uid":3136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:59:21.000Z","msg":"樓主咪又係d思想唔成熟既小學雞 如果真係做撚到嘢 就唔會係度上連登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你覺得呢度風氣唔好 代表你自己唔適合呢個討論區姐 你唔係天真到個個都要同你思想一樣樣啊？<br />\nbtw 都係果句 走啦，冇人留你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f316cb9cd41a7c1d63a65fb0c04853187e137c","tid":360123,"uid":1147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:11:29.000Z","msg":"我本身鍾意睇政治、國際關係既野，但好少上時事台、政事台...入需啲post低質到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身邊有啲frd政治冷感，但我都唔會怪佢地，亦唔會強人所難，通常都係叫佢睇多啲新聞、起碼知道發生緊乜野事咁"},{"pid":"b8c10e8f4c1e2b09f81cdf3fb7902efd5277299a","tid":360123,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"連登等於香港？"},{"pid":"75c5aca414e251b813c7e86f81afec59393bf31d","tid":360123,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:20:19.000Z","msg":"你自己入時事台同政事台睇下再講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}